For build requirements see poldek.spec. 

Required trurlib may be downloaded from PLD ftp site:
<ftp://ftp.pld.org.pl/PLD-1.0/SRPMS/SRPMS/trurlib-*.src.rpm>
<ftp://ftp.pld.org.pl/PLD-1.0/$ARCH/PLD/RPMS/trurlib-*.rpm>

or from CVS repository
cvs -d :pserver:cvs@anoncvs.pld.org.pl:/cvsroot get -r CURRENT \ 
	installer/trurlib

To build it do:
$ cd installer/trurlib && ./configure && make && make install

After trurlib installation try in poldek/

$ ./configure && make

